MODIFICATIONS

ArcherDB extends TigerBeetle's core with geospatial capabilities for
fleet tracking, logistics, and real-time location applications:

- GeoEvent state machine for location data (replacing Account/Transfer)
- S2 geometry indexing for spatial queries
- RAM-based entity index for O(1) latest-position lookups
- Specialized query operations (radius, polygon, entity history)
- Client SDK extensions for geospatial operations

See the CHANGELOG for detailed modification history.
